        <p class="lead">PotatoScan — an AI tool that lets farmers snap a potato leaf photo and get an instant disease diagnosis with 97% accuracy, treatment recommendations, and multilingual support (EN/HI/BN). No lab. No agronomist. No waiting.</p>
